description:
Absconding diamond billionaire Mehul Choksi was arrested in Belgium in April - a few days later - a Sunday fire in Mumbai's ED office destroyed a lot of records pertaining to the case. This is not the first time that Choksi has come close to be extradited to India - will he escape this time like he did in Antigua? Or is the Govt of India better prepared?
